text: Jan unemployment rates ranged from 1.9% ND to 5.3% in NV.
RI and VT saw the highest house price growth between Q4 2022 and Q4 2023.
State real GDP in Q3 2023 was higher than in Q3 2022 in all states except DE.
Jan average private weekly earnings in states ranged from $889 in MS to $1,377 in WA.
Total private sector jobs in Jan 2024 were above Jan 2019 levels in 44 states.
Q3 2023 retail real GDP growth over the year was at least 8% in every state and DC.
Wyoming saw a 10-year low in its unemployment rate in Jan 2024.
Manufacturing jobs in Jan 2024 were below Jan 2023 levels in 23 states.
HI housing prices reached a decade low in Q4 2023.
